# scripts/commands/config.sh flattens config/smackerel.yaml with a LINE-BASED
# awk pass that requires the documented single-line compact-JSON SST values
# (e.g. retrieval.routing.contracts, services.ml.model_memory_profiles) to stay
# on ONE line. Prettier — or any formatter driven through Prettier's ignore file
# (including the VS Code Prettier extension) — that reflows them into multi-line
# block form makes the key un-findable and breaks EVERY ./smackerel.sh command
# ("Missing config key: ..."). Keep this file out of all formatter passes.
config/smackerel.yaml
